4
00:00:25,800 --> 00:00:30,120
The people of Liore are ethnically very similar to Ishbal.

5
00:00:30,120 --> 00:00:31,880
The folks at Central

6
00:00:31,880 --> 00:00:35,540
must not have thought of them as being the same kind of people as themselves.

7
00:00:35,540 --> 00:00:37,220
That is not true!

8
00:00:38,100 --> 00:00:41,190
I am going to complete 
the Philosopher's Stone

9
00:00:41,190 --> 00:00:44,480
for the sake of all people 
who suffer under tyranny.

10
00:00:44,480 --> 00:00:45,470
Wait...

11
00:00:46,370 --> 00:00:47,230
Wait!

12
00:01:14,470 --> 00:01:18,140
This one is on a whole other level 
compared with the ones Tucker was creating.

13
00:01:18,140 --> 00:01:21,200
Is this the legacy of 
the 5th Laboratory?

14
00:01:22,470 --> 00:01:27,420
All of these things were known to you 
and Colonel Archer, weren't they, Major?

15
00:01:27,420 --> 00:01:31,020
What the hell are you guys hiding? We've had enough already.

16
00:01:31,020 --> 00:01:32,570
Please stop!

17
00:01:33,660 --> 00:01:34,670
Al-kun...

18
00:01:36,660 --> 00:01:39,900
Major Armstrong doesn't have anything to do with this.

19
00:01:39,900 --> 00:01:42,400
<i>I'm</i> the one who was 
harboring Martel-san.

20
00:01:42,400 --> 00:01:44,580
Wh-What are you talking about, 
Alphonse-kun?

21
00:01:44,840 --> 00:01:47,340
There is something that 
I've come to understand.

22
00:01:47,340 --> 00:01:49,650
I can't say anything 
about it now,

23
00:01:49,650 --> 00:01:52,670
but please, everyone, 
no more fighting.

24
00:01:54,330 --> 00:01:56,880
Please, don't fight.

25
00:02:05,920 --> 00:02:10,440
Major, I know that you're trying to carry on where Hughes left off.

26
00:02:11,940 --> 00:02:15,440
"You can just make your way to the top without having to know about anything."

27
00:02:15,710 --> 00:02:18,900
"I will investigate what's happening behind the scenes myself."

28
00:02:19,670 --> 00:02:20,450
Isn't that right?

29
00:02:24,020 --> 00:02:27,160
I'm terribly sorry. 
Right now, I'm not...

30
00:02:35,310 --> 00:02:36,300
Al!

31
00:02:36,300 --> 00:02:37,550
Martel-san!

32
00:02:37,550 --> 00:02:39,550
Al, listen to me, and tell Ed, too!

33
00:02:39,800 --> 00:02:41,670
Whatever, just get inside me!

34
00:02:45,710 --> 00:02:47,100
Al, listen...

35
00:02:47,100 --> 00:02:48,600
Martel-san, what on earth is it?

36
00:02:48,600 --> 00:02:50,600
Liore is going to be 
turned into another Ishbal!

37
00:02:50,600 --> 00:02:52,110
What do you mean?

38
00:02:52,110 --> 00:02:54,610
That man—the Führer—

39
00:02:55,980 --> 00:02:57,190
is a homunculus!

40
00:03:11,880 --> 00:03:17,620
Far away, far away, our dreams will never fade

41
